Class RandomListGenerator<T>

Type Parameters:

All Implemented Interfaces:

public class RandomListGenerator<T> extends Object implements IGenerator<T>
Generates values randomly. An associative array of values and probabilities is provided in the constructor.

nikolay.grozev
